div.div: English: Flag of Georgia, taken from the xrmap flag collection 2.7. The flag's colors have been corrected based on an image found on the Georgia Secretary of State's Web site. The font face of the phrase "IN GOD WE TRUST" has been changed to w:en:Times New Roman, since that matches the Georgia Secretary of State image.
